I"l	<h1 id="adding-packages">adding packages</h1>

<h2 id="list-recipes-installed">list recipes installed</h2>
<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>composer recipes
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="annotation">annotation</h2>
<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>composer require annotations
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>to add route via annotation</p>

<h2 id="web-debug-toolbar">Web Debug Toolbar</h2>
<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>composer require debug <span class="nt">--dev</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>we got the web debug toolbar</p>

<h2 id="http-client">Http Client</h2>
<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>composer require symfony/http-client
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>Provides powerful methods to fetch HTTP resources synchronously or asynchronously</p>

<h2 id="asset-component">asset component</h2>
<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>composer require symfony/asset
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>to access files through asset</p>

<h3 id="exemple">exemple</h3>

<div class="language-html highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nt">&lt;link</span> <span class="na">rel=</span><span class="s">"stylesheet"</span> <span class="na">href=</span><span class="s">"{{ asset('css/app.css') }}"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="twig">twig</h2>
<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>composer require symfony/twig-pack
    or
composer require templates      // flex aliases
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>create a templates repository and install twig pack</p>

<h2 id="make">make</h2>

<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>composer require <span class="nt">--dev</span> symfony/maker-bundle
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>now we can use make in the CLI</p>

<h2 id="remove-packages">remove packages</h2>
<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>composer remove <span class="o">[</span>package_name_or_recipe_name]
</code></pre></div></div>
:ET